I"Í<h1 id="infrastructure-architecture">Infrastructure architecture</h1>

<p>OpenProject is an open-source core and available for users and customers as three different distributions available under two different infrastructure:</p>

<ul>
  <li>the on-premises <a href="https://www.openproject.org/download-and-installation/">Community Edition</a> and <a href="https://www.openproject.org/enterprise-edition/">Enterprise Edition with Enterprise Support</a> which runs on your own hardware</li>
  <li>the <a href="https://www.openproject.org/hosting/">Cloud Edition</a> hosted distribution which is hosted and maintained by OpenProject</li>
</ul>

